  glimpse-4.17.4.ebuild, +metadata.xml:
  Added RDEPEND=!dev-libs/tre due to both providing /usr/bin/agrep. Thanks to
  John Hampton in bug #53250

*glimpse-4.17.4 (06 Dec 2003)

  21 Apr 2004; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> :
  Add gcc-3.x patch #42970 by Joe Khoobyar.  Also cleanup ebuild so that
  the package uses user's CFLAGS.

  16 Feb 2004; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> glimpse-4.15-r1.ebuild,
  glimpse-4.17.4.ebuild:
  add alpha and ia64 keywords

  08 Jan 2004; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> glimpse-4.17.4.ebuild:
  added iuse=static

  06 Dec 2003; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> glimpse-4.17.4.ebuild:
  bump

  05 Dec 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> glimpse-4.15-r1.ebuild:
